  Dear Webmaster,

I can say this is the coolest website out there. I can't say I like the art
being arranged in linear fashion. Links like Art, More  Art and Even more
fine art were some of my favorites.
I thought it was a nice juxtaposition to see some art from 1654 next to
some fabulous sci-fi peice from 1970.

Anyway that's the two cents of someone on the internet.


Thank you kindly,

                 Raul

